[{"image":"/images/story97_c_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_c_m.mp3",
"text":"怎樣在快餐店裡買食物"},
{"image":"/images/story97_p1_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_p1_m.mp3",
"text":"我們到麥當勞、肯德基這類快餐店吃東西，要自己到櫃檯買食物、飲料"},
{"image":"/images/story97_p2_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_p2_m.mp3",
"text":"大人知道怎樣在快餐店裡買食物，可以幫助小朋友學習這些步驟"},
{"image":"/images/story97_p3_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_p3_m.mp3",
"text":"一、到櫃檯前選擇跟隨哪一隊買食物"},
{"image":"/images/story97_p4_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_p4_m.mp3",
"text":"二、一個接一個排隊"},
{"image":"/images/story97_p5_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_p5_m.mp3",
"text":"三、輪到我的時候，向店員說出要買的東西"},
{"image":"/images/story97_p6_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_p6_m.mp3",
"text":"四、付錢給店員"},
{"image":"/images/story97_p7_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_p7_m.mp3",
"text":"五、等候店員把食物拿給我們"},
{"image":"/images/story97_p8_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_p8_m.mp3",
"text":"六、把食物拿回座位慢慢吃"},
{"image":"/images/story97_p9_t.png",
"audio":"/audios/story97_p9_m.mp3",
"text":"如果我能按照跟從這些步驟去做，便能在快餐店買東西吃"}]
